Package com.sanyavertolet.interview.math.expressions

Class ValueExpression

java.lang.Object
com.sanyavertolet.interview.math.expressions.Expression
com.sanyavertolet.interview.math.expressions.ValueExpression
public class ValueExpression extends Expression
Represents an expression that holds a constant Value. The ValueExpression class is a specific type of Expression that encapsulates a single value.
